      • removed

        protected void removed(Object key,
                       Object value)
        This method is an override point to detect when a key is removed from the cache. If something must be done when a key is removed, override this method. The method is called after the key and value are removed from the cache. This implementation does nothing.
        Parameters:
        key - The key that has been removed
        value - The value that has been removed
